OL,3,CTwo men appear in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after stabbing
OL,6,FTwo men have appeared in court accused
OL,7,Fof attempting to murder a man who is
OL,8,Falleged to have been stabbed to the
OL,9,Fhead, face and body at an address in
OL,10,FCarlisle over the weekend.
OL,12,FAlex Steventon, 46, and Connor
OL,13,FChallinor, 29, are jointly accused of
OL,14,Fattempting to murder the victim on
OL,15,FSunday March 29.
OL,17,FThey appeared at Carlisle Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt on Tuesday March 31.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
