OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774980702
OL,3,CTwo men appear in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after stabbing
OL,6,FDuring a seven-minute court hearing, a
OL,7,Fprosecutor gave a brief outline of the
OL,8,Fincident and alleged that the man had
OL,9,Fbeen stabbed multiple times ` to the
OL,10,Fhead, face and body ` and suffered
OL,11,Fserious injuries.
OL,13,FA Cumbria Police spokesperson said
OL,14,Fyesterday that the man had been
OL,15,Ftreated in hospital and later
OL,16,Fdischarged.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
