PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774980702
OL,3,CTwo men appear in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after stabbing
OL,6,FSteventon, who wore a dark coloured
OL,7,Fpadded jacket, and Challinor, dressed
OL,8,Fin a black jumper, appeared side-by-
OL,9,Fside in a court dock flanked by
OL,10,Fsecurity staff members.
OL,12,FBoth spoke to confirm their names,
OL,13,Fdates of birth and addresses.
OL,15,FNeither man was asked to indicate a
OL,16,Fplea to the attempted murder charge,
OL,17,Fwhich is classed as "indictable only"
OL,18,F- meaning that it is so serious that
OL,19,Fit must be dealt with at a crown court.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
