CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774980702
OL,3,CTwo men appear in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after stabbing
OL,6,FA bench of three magistrates formally
OL,7,Fsent the case to Carlisle Crown Court.
OL,9,FCumbria Police says it was made aware
OL,10,Fthat a man in his 30 had sustained a
OL,11,Fnumber of suspected stab wounds at
OL,12,F3:24am on Sunday, 29th March.
OL,14,FThese were wounds reported to have
OL,15,Foccurred at an address in Edward
OL,16,FStreet, which runs parallel to London
OL,17,FRoad.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
