CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774980702
OL,3,CTwo men appear in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after stabbing
OL,6,FOfficers made five arrests in the
OL,7,Faftermath and, as they launched an
OL,8,Finvestigation, made a public appeal
OL,9,Ffor witnesses and information.
OL,11,FCity-based pair Steventon, of Denton
OL,12,FStreet, and Challinor, who gave his
OL,13,Faddress as Sybil Street, are next due
OL,14,Fto appear in front of a judge at the
OL,15,Fcrown court for a plea and trial
OL,16,Fpreparation hearing on 1st May.
OL,18,FIn the meantime both men have been
OL,19,Fremanded in custody.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
